-- Government to Consider 26% Foreign Investment in Airlines, Times Reports
-- Abhishek Shanker
-- 2010-07-08T02:11:59Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-08/government-to-consider-26-foreign-investment-in-airlines-times-reports.html

          
          
               India will consider allowing 
foreign airlines to invest up to 26 percent in local carriers, 
the Times of India reported citing Civial Aviation Minister 
Praful Patel.  
